		<title>How Hypnosis Helps to Develop a Positive Attitude</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/energyandmotivation/feed/~3/cpRPzUT0YlI/</link>
		<comments>http://energyandmotivation.com/5741/positive-attitude-hypnosis/#comments</comments>
